{"tid":1406432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「後續討論」三罷後應否設死線","createTime":"2019-08-04T13:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T22:10:43.000Z","uid":31631,"like":79,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"39aff848ecf1c5938964b86394d86f144fc7fe16","tid":1406432,"uid":31631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"三罷之後 估計到星期二 一切又會如常<br />\n再loop星期六日既示威<br />\n<br />\n相信有唔少人都覺得再咁落去唔係辦法<br />\n每個星期睇住手足流血 被捕<br />\n每個香港人都好心痛 同時 無力<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎喇 我地係咪應該設死線<br />\n例如 要求政府48小時內回應五大訴求<br />\n否則 無限期罷工或以武力衝擊<br />\n<br />\n我知道無限期罷工係無乜可能<br />\n而武力衝擊我地係83展現左比政府知 我地係會玩火<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論 如果唔係又會進入瓶頸位<br />\n要搵個大noise既事件煲大佢 突破瓶頸<br />\n<br />\n而我相信85罷工係一個好好既機會<br />\n和理非既殺手鐧係咪罷工<br />\n仲有無其他出路？"},{"pid":"9d5dc875677bd82e45ec3664bf6771375eba397b","tid":1406432,"uid":31631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934d887cb98f7a6d5ad4a8056453b340bf70dfc3","tid":1406432,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該入一入黎幫手推post</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【8.5三罷】如果朝早所有人遊車河!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cc3YftZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCc3YftZ.png&h=73d6d6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUfS7Za.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUfS7Za.png&h=2961d9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74af10d9b96e0e5f1e781d001d1aa93f